  <brief_title>MESS-study MRSA Eradication Study Skåne</brief_title>
  <acronym>MESS</acronym>
  <official_title>MESS- MRSA Eradication Study Skåne. A Comparison Between Systemic Antibiotic Treatment in Combination With Topical Mupirocintreatment With Only Topical Mupiroicintreatment to Eradicate MRSA in Throat Carriers</official_title>
  <sponsors>
