  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether systemic antibiotic treatment with
      rifampicin and clindamycine or trimethoprim-sulfa in addition to topical treatment with
      mupirocin is more effective than only topical treatment to eradicate MRSA in throatcarriers
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
